    "body": "After doing some UX design work, I think there are two semi-orthogonal states we need to track:\n1. selected\n2. focused\n\nHere are some state diagrams to show the various transitions between the product space of these states. Notice that some of the product states are not possible and need to be handled specially.\n\n![focusjump1](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/27600/663901/c5b8b41a-d779-11e2-93ba-9b3bbc00daf7.jpg)\n![focusjump2](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/27600/663902/c7f262d0-d779-11e2-8939-bdc5748b2b40.jpg)\n"
  },
