    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Questions:\n- Should `Shift-Enter` on a code cell call `unfocus` the cell but leave it selected? We currently select and focus the next cell.\n- Should we still add, select and focus a new cell at the end of the notebook when the last cell is run?\n- Do we want to use `Enter` to focus the selected cell, even for code cells?\n"
